${h3}0.16 - 1998/05/28:${h3end}

New features:${pul}

${bullet}This version compiles for OS/2, with EMX. This entailed substantial
${indent}changes to the Makefile (q.v.), as well as some code.

${bullet}The environment variable MMAIL can now be used instead of HOME, to specify
