${bullet}Truly automatic packet recognition, by packet contents instead of name.
${indent}Patch by Robert Vukovic.

${bullet}Internal ANSI viewer. Works on all platforms (except that it sometimes
${indent}segfaults when scrolling, under OS/2). Much better than the \"less\"
${indent}viewer, and it will form the basis of new file list and bulletin
${indent}viewers.${ulend}

Bug fixes and such:${pul}

